headline: T-Mobile to Host Q2 2025 Earnings Call on July 23, 2025
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., June 20, 2025--T-Mobile US, Inc. (NASDAQ: TMUS) looks forward to discussing second quarter 2025 financial and operational results on Wednesday, July 23, 2025, at 4:30 p.m. Eastern Daylight Time (EDT). The call will be accessible via dial-in with pre-registration as well as a webcast link on the Company’s Investor Relations website at https://investor.t-mobile.com. The earnings release, Investor Factbook, and other related materials will be available at approximately 4:05 p.m. ED
